Description: Load scanpy h5ad files into R and launch an interactive QC
    dashboard for single-cell RNA-seq data. Provides h5ad I/O, H5AD
    validation, cell filtering with auto-detected QC metrics, interactive
    UMAP exploration, and batch QC reports.
